321
00:11:46,431 --> 00:11:47,664
It is.

322
00:11:47,666 --> 00:11:49,065
You're the best dad ever.

323
00:11:49,067 --> 00:11:52,569
Yeah. Uh, hold that thought.

324
00:11:52,571 --> 00:11:54,904
