be a "lehver."

364
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:27,163
Let's see, a "lehver,"
a "lehver"...

365
00:13:27,165 --> 00:13:28,565
Everybody hold on!

366
00:13:28,567 --> 00:13:30,300
